00:25:05,556 --> 00:25:06,417
The first is chips.

530
00:25:08,818 --> 00:25:10,399
First thing you have to do when you walk into a casino

531
00:25:10,419 --> 00:25:12,880
is you have to exchange your money for an abstract token.

532
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:14,541
And a lot of studies have shown

533
00:25:15,001 --> 00:25:16,862
that when people start exchanging tokens

534
00:25:16,902 --> 00:25:17,982
instead of exchanging money,

535
00:25:18,403 --> 00:25:20,224
that they don't ascribe the same value to it.

536
00:25:20,404 --> 00:25:22,185
It gets abstracted and.

537
00:25:22,975 --> 00:25:27,138
they get subtracted and they don't assign as much value to it.

538
00:25:27,738 --> 00:25:32,602
And casinos specifically will try to make it difficult for you to convert.

539
00:25:32,702 --> 00:25:34,103
It's easy for one-way trip,

540
00:25:34,123 --> 00:25:36,644
but you can't go back the other way also once you convert to chips.

541
00:25:37,825 --> 00:25:38,986
If you sit down at a blackjack table,

542
00:25:39,006 --> 00:25:41,408
I can give $200 to a blackjack dealer and they'll hand me a stack of chips,

543
00:25:41,448 --> 00:25:42,909
but if I want to turn my chips back into money,

544
00:25:42,929 --> 00:25:44,110
I can't do it right there.

545
00:25:44,150 --> 00:25:45,651
I got to pick up and I got to walk across.

546
00:25:47,732 --> 00:25:49,553
But the other big thing is also jackpots.

547
00:25:50,341 --> 00:25:52,922
People are really bad at dealing with big numbers

548
00:25:53,423 --> 00:25:54,603
and small probabilities,

549
00:25:55,444 --> 00:25:57,825
and the casinos are starting to take advantage of that.

550
00:25:58,605 --> 00:25:59,766
Most of the games now, if you go,

551
00:25:59,806 --> 00:26:00,886
if you've been to casinos lately,

552
00:26:00,946 --> 00:26:02,687
blackjack tables and a lot of these new games,

