00:26:02,747 --> 00:26:05,129
they all have these little jackpot bonus bets.

554
00:26:05,489 --> 00:26:06,229
It's very common.

555
00:26:06,269 --> 00:26:07,170
People like that.

556
00:26:07,590 --> 00:26:09,471
People like the idea that they're gonna get a lot of money,

557
00:26:09,871 --> 00:26:12,993
and that helps them overcome this idea of loss aversion.

