00:26:54,748 --> 00:26:58,210
Powerball used to be about 100 million to one odds to win,

573
00:26:58,230 --> 00:27:01,773
and they keep changing the game every couple of years,

574
00:27:02,173 --> 00:27:05,575
and now it's like 300 million to one to win.

575
00:27:07,368 --> 00:27:09,209
because they like these big jackpots.

