00:27:12,611 --> 00:27:15,493
or .000001% chance to win,

578
00:27:16,173 --> 00:27:17,674
mentally they put that in the same bucket.

579
00:27:18,455 --> 00:27:19,836
Just like the $3,000 and the $4,000

