00:27:22,397 --> 00:27:23,878
Once probabilities get really high,

582
00:27:24,179 --> 00:27:26,360
million to one, 200 million to one, 300 million to one,

583
00:27:26,800 --> 00:27:28,781
people have no idea of what that is.

