00:27:42,644 --> 00:27:45,406
They went into a classroom in Chicago,

588
00:27:45,446 --> 00:27:46,487
and they gave three different.

589
00:27:47,989 --> 00:27:50,670
bonus plans to different groups of teachers.

590
00:27:51,090 --> 00:27:53,031
One was just the control group, no bonus plan.

