00:28:37,832 --> 00:28:39,513
and I decided that it was just never gonna work.

613
00:28:40,973 --> 00:28:44,214
But the point remains that giving something to people,

614
00:28:44,714 --> 00:28:46,715
you know, just most people when they see this idea,

615
00:28:47,529 --> 00:28:50,511
of getting a bonus at the start of the year and you have to give it back if you don't

616
00:28:50,551 --> 00:28:56,195
perform. It's very stressful. Even though again financially it's really the same thing

