788
00:37:12,921 --> 00:37:14,581
that they ascribe it more value

789
00:37:15,221 --> 00:37:18,162
than if it was just off to the side or they didn't have it.

790
00:37:18,922 --> 00:37:20,442
The classic study that they did on this

791
00:37:20,502 --> 00:37:21,843
is they had participants do something

792
00:37:22,483 --> 00:37:23,543
and just in the beginning of it,

