00:37:23,583 --> 00:37:25,903
they gave them a mug as a prize for it,

794
00:37:25,923 --> 00:37:27,644
they gave them a candy bar as a prize for it,

795
00:37:28,444 --> 00:37:30,644
and they then at the end of the study

796
00:37:30,704 --> 00:37:32,645
asked people if they wanted to switch to the other prize.

797
00:37:33,485 --> 00:37:34,585
Most people wouldn't switch.

798
00:37:35,785 --> 00:37:37,266
Even if they asked them beforehand,

799
00:37:37,386 --> 00:37:38,526
would you rather have a mug or would you rather have

800
00:37:38,546 --> 00:37:40,446
a candy bar, and they got the one they didn't want.

801
00:37:40,986 --> 00:37:42,127
Once they got that and they had it.

802
00:37:43,225 --> 00:37:46,830
that it was something that they just wanted to stick with.

